fields.name: OUT_md5
fields.expression:
MD5(
	ApplicationNumber
	||PolicyNumber
	||SystemId
	||
	IIF(ISNULL(CustomerNumber),'',CustomerNumber ) 
	||
IIF(ISNULL(CommercialName),'',CommercialName)
	||
IIF(ISNULL(EmailAddr),'',EmailAddr)
	||
IIF(ISNULL(TransactionCd),'',TransactionCd)
||Status||TypeCd||TO_CHAR(AddDt)
||AddTm
||
IIF(ISNULL(to_char(CloseDt)),'',to_char(CloseDt))
||
IIF(ISNULL(CloseTm),'',CloseTm)
||
IIF(ISNULL(to_char(ChangeDt)),'',to_char(ChangeDt))
||
IIF(ISNULL(To_Char(EffectiveDt)),'',To_Char(EffectiveDt))
||
IIF(ISNULL(To_Char(ExpirationDt)),'',To_Char(ExpirationDt))
||
IIF(ISNULL(to_Char(InceptionDt)),'',to_Char(InceptionDt))
||
IIF(ISNULL(to_char(UpdateDt)),'',to_char(UpdateDt))
||
IIF(ISNULL(CarrierCd),'',CarrierCd)
||
IIF(ISNULL(AddUser),'',AddUser)
||
IIF(ISNULL(PolicyVersion),'',PolicyVersion)
||IIF(ISNULL(SubmittedDt),'',to_char(SubmittedDt))
||IIF(ISNULL(ControllingStateCd), '', ControllingStateCd)
||IIF(ISNULL(SubTypeCd), '', SubTypeCd)
||IIF(ISNULL(LineCd), '', LineCd)
||IIF(ISNULL(AgencyCd), '', AgencyCd)
||IIF(ISNULL(AgencyCommercialName), '', AgencyCommercialName)
||IIF(ISNULL(LOB_Display_Group_Desc), '', LOB_Display_Group_Desc)
||SourceCd
)

fields.name: out_PolicyForm
fields.expression:
IIF(IN(SubTypeCd,'BOP', 'BOP1'), 'Standard',
IIF(SubTypeCd = 'BOP2', 'Special',
IIF(SubTypeCd = 'ExcessLiability', 'Excess',
IIF(SubTypeCd = 'UmbrellaLiability','Commercial Umbrella',
IIF(SubTypeCd = 'UmbrellaBasic', 'PersonalUmbrella', SubTypeCd)))))

fields.name: OUT_Flag
fields.expression:
IIF(ISNULL(IN_QuoteNumber) AND  Status<>'In Process'
AND IN_RecFlag='NewQuoteRec', 'MissedRecord',
IIF(ISNULL(IN_QuoteNumber) ,'New',
IIF(IN_QuoteHashKey<>calc_md5,'Changed','UnChanged')))

object.customQuery:
SELECT Quoteinfo_Stg.SystemId, 
Quoteinfo_Stg.ApplicationNumber, 
Quoteinfo_Stg.CustomerNumber, 
Quoteinfo_Stg.Status, 
Quoteinfo_Stg.TypeCd, 
Quoteinfo_Stg.AddDt, 
Quoteinfo_Stg.AddTm, 
Quoteinfo_Stg.AddUser, 
Quoteinfo_Stg.UpdateDt, 
Quoteinfo_Stg.SubmittedDt, 
Quoteinfo_Stg.CloseDt, 
Quoteinfo_Stg.CloseTm, 
Quoteinfo_Stg.CarrierCd, 
Quoteinfo_Stg.ChangeDt,
Quoteinfo_Stg.ControllingStateCd,
Quoteinfo_Stg.EffectiveDt, 
Quoteinfo_Stg.ExpirationDt, 
Quoteinfo_Stg.WrittenPremiumAmt,
Quoteinfo_Stg.InceptionDt,
Quoteinfo_Stg.ProviderCd,
Quoteinfo_Stg.SubTypeCd, 
Quoteinfo_Stg.TransactionCd, 
Quoteinfo_Stg.CommercialName, 
Quoteinfo_Stg.EmailAddr, 
basicpolicyapp_stg.PolicyNumber, 
basicpolicyapp_stg.PolicyVersion, 
basicpolicyapp_stg.QuoteNumber, 
Application_Stg.ApplicationNumber,
Line_Stg.LineCd
FROM
 dbo.Quoteinfo_Stg inner join dbo.Application_Stg
 on Quoteinfo_Stg.SystemId=Application_Stg.SystemId
 left join  dbo.basicpolicyapp_stg
 on basicpolicyapp_stg.SystemId=Quoteinfo_Stg.SystemId
 left join dbo.Line_Stg
 on Quoteinfo_Stg.SystemId = Line_Stg.SystemId
and line_stg.CMMContainer='Application'
